==English==
===Phrase===
'''Aye Aye, Sir'''
#(''nautical'') The [[correct]] and [[seamanlike]] [[reply]], [[onboard]] a [[Royal Navy]] (or U.S Navy) [[ship]], on [[receipt]] of an [[order]] from any [[officer]] of any [[sex]]. It means I hear and will comply, Sir.

===See also===
*[[Ahoy]] - where one reply to this hail is '''aye aye'''
*[[aye-aye]] - a type of lemur

